    <h2 class="text-5xl underline mb-8 font-bold text-black mt-14">Eyemorse</h2>
    <a href="https://github.com/jeffersonnjohan/Eyemorse" target="_blank"><button class="mb-10 bg-brown1 text-brown4 py-5 px-8 rounded-full text-md hover:bg-black hover:text-white duration-200">Lihat Project Saya di GitHub -></button></a>
    <img src="/img/eyemorse.jpg" alt="Image 1" class = "w-1/2 m-auto mb-8">
    <p class="mb-8 text-justify">Eyemorse is AI Application spesifically Computer Vision to convert eye blinking to morse code. With the application, we can send morse code with just our eye. This project was done at 3th Cawu for Artificial Intelligence Course with Mr. Ivan Halim Parmonangan.</p>
    <img src="/img/ipk5Foto.jpg" alt="Image 1" class = "w-1/2 m-auto mb-8">
